name: Perfect Match
overview: Couples who prove their compatibility gain the power to make or break other matches in this strategic and seductive dating competition.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Couples who prove their compatibility gain the power to make or break other matches in this strategic and seductive dating competition.

tagline: In this game of love, they'll play by their own rules.

episodes.name: Love is the End
episodes.overview: Ten single stars from popular Netflix reality series gather at a villa to find their first matches. Two friends opt to prioritize strategy over romance.

episodes.name: It's About the Chase
episodes.overview: A confident new contestant threatens a budding romance. During an unusual kissing challenge, the couples swap spit and surprise themselves.

episodes.name: Strike a Match
episodes.overview: The last challenge's winning couple picks new dates that make waves, and tension boils over between two women with eyes on the same guy.

episodes.name: Unfinished Business
episodes.overview: Four people agree to a surprising partner swap, but will it cause heartache? An auction challenge has the couples betting on their chemistry.

episodes.name: Blind-Sided
episodes.overview: After an eye-opening round of new dates, one seemingly solid pair falls apart while another decides to re-match for a second try.

episodes.name: Love is Savage
episodes.overview: First-date sparks fly during a spa treatment and fizzle at a wine tasting. The couples compete to squeeze out a win in a sopping wet sponge race.

episodes.name: Circling Back
episodes.overview: A contestant's recent ex causes trouble in paradise. Two women start to have doubts about how compatible their matches really are.

episodes.name: Mixes and Matches
episodes.overview: In a first for the house, a potential same-sex couple hits it off at their first meeting. Someone who's been unlucky in love considers a big risk.

episodes.name: Love It or Leave It
episodes.overview: Chaos reigns in the villa as exes get jealous, a late-night make-out session causes conflict and old crushes make new comebacks.

episodes.name: Making Waves
episodes.overview: The couples learn a lot about each other during the final compatibility challenge and frank conversations at the house. One contestant faces doubts.

episodes.name: Back in the Mix
episodes.overview: After a dramatic night, the house gets ready to welcome back familiar faces for a party that will test how strong their bonds really are.

episodes.name: Game, Set, Perfect Match
episodes.overview: Last dates lead to emotional conversations and a huge surprise before the ultimate decision: who makes the most perfect match of all?

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Couples who prove their compatibility gain the power to make or break other matches in this strategic and seductive dating competition.

episodes.name: Ready, Set, Match
episodes.overview: Ten singles arrive in Tulum and break the ice with some dicey dares. Fledging flirtationships hang in the balance during a physical challenge.

episodes.name: Kiss and Tell
episodes.overview: The couples dive in lips first for the kissing challenge. A surprise date creates drama for one pair, and two sets of matches decide to shake things up.

episodes.name: Chaos Theory
episodes.overview: The boardroom becomes the war room when one couple stirs the pot. One contestant's reputation returns to haunt their current match  and their new date.

episodes.name: Truth Bombs
episodes.overview: A new match is sealed with a kiss, and the contestants are tested on how well they know one another. One couple's sweet evening turns sour.

episodes.name: Shakeups & Breakups
episodes.overview: A tough night turns into a testy morning in the boardroom. Matches and the matchless make bold moves as one single's sudden interest raises doubts.

episodes.name: Seeing Eye to Eye
episodes.overview: The couples hit the beach to test their teamwork skills. One contestant turns their attention toward a former crush. A new arrival makes a splash.

episodes.name: Love Is Blindfolded
episodes.overview: Trust and vulnerability are key as the couples try to untangle themselves during a compatibility challenge. One boardroom decision ushers in a storm.

episodes.name: He Said, She Said
episodes.overview: There's trouble in Tulum when the guys and gals enjoy their respective days out  only to be interrupted by some flirtatious party crashers.

episodes.name: To Tell the Truth
episodes.overview: Ahead of the final vote, couples find their futures hanging in the balance when a tense mixer brings romance and drama  plus potential new matches.

episodes.name: Perfectly Ever After
episodes.overview: Hot dates lead to hard conversations as the couples face their futures. But among unlikely pairs and fiery flings, who will be crowned the perfect match?
